1. Moj otac *mete* dvorište svaki vikend. (My father sweeps the yard every weekend.)
2. *Metla* koju si kupio nije dovoljno kvalitetna. (The broom you bought is not of good enough quality.)
3. Kada *ometeš* prašinu, obavezno otvori prozor. (When you sweep up the dust, make sure to open the window.)
4. Policajac je *ometen* zbog buke i nije čuo kada mu je prilazio napadač. (The policeman was distracted by the noise and didn't hear the attacker approaching him.)
5. Neki ljudi *ometu* druge tokom sastanka nepotrebnim pitanjima. (Some people interrupt others during a meeting with unnecessary questions.)
6. Ovaj problem neće biti lako *ometnuti* pod tepih. (This problem won't be easy to sweep under the rug.)